### Get Auth Token
# @name login
POST {{BACKEND_DOMAIN}}/api/v1/auth/email/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "{{TEST_EMAIL}}",
  "password": "{{TEST_PASSWORD}}"
}

### Set token variable from login response
@token = {{login.token}}

### ===========================================
### PATCH DIVISIONS ENDPOINTS (UPDATE)
### ===========================================

### Update Division (Basic Fields)
PATCH {{BACKEND_DOMAIN}}/api/v1/divisions/1
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "division_name": "Updated Technology Division",
  "remarks": "Updated remarks for technology division"
}

### Update Division (Status Change)
PATCH {{BACKEND_DOMAIN}}/api/v1/divisions/1
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "status": "Active"
}

### Update Division (Complete Update)
PATCH {{BACKEND_DOMAIN}}/api/v1/divisions/1
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "division_code": "01",
  "division_name": "Advanced Technology Division",
  "remarks": "Updated technology division with enhanced capabilities",
  "status": "Active"
}

### Update Division (Multiple Fields)
PATCH {{BACKEND_DOMAIN}}/api/v1/divisions/1
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "division_name": "Strategic Technology Division",
  "remarks": "Updated strategic technology division"
}
